title: New Books of July 2017 Part 1 (Treasure Trove) [Trinketbell]
description:
These are major Cozy Mystery, Harlequin Books and Romance, published within July. 

List is too big for the description, so if you want a list of books without getting the torrent, visit https://hastebin.com/tifivovugi.md


There are some books that are from previous months, added in, and they are the following:

Blood Red, White and Blue - Kathleen Delaney - January 2017
Dirty Dancing at the Picture House By The Sea - Holly Hepburn - June 2017
Protecting His Interests - Rock, Suzanne - June 2017
Practice Makes Perfect - Penny Parkes - June 2017


♥ ♥ ♥ ♥ ♥ ♥ Happy reading. Please seed and keep alive!! ♥ ♥ ♥ ♥ ♥ ♥
